verses.verse: <S%H1984>Praise<s%> <S%H3050>Yah!<s%> <S%H1984>Praise<s%> <S%H410>God<s%> in his <S%H6944>sanctuary!<s%> <S%H1984>Praise<s%> him in his <S%H7549>heavens<s%> for his acts of <S%H5797>power!<s%>
<S%H1984>Praise<s%> him for his mighty <S%H1369>acts!<s%> <S%H1984>Praise<s%> him according to his <S%H7230>excellent<s%> <S%H1433>greatness!<s%>
<S%H1984>Praise<s%> him with the <S%H8629>sounding<s%> of the <S%H7782>trumpet!<s%> <S%H1984>Praise<s%> him with <S%H5035>harp<s%> and <S%H5035>lyre!<s%>
<S%H1984>Praise<s%> him with <S%H8596>tambourine<s%> and <S%H4234>dancing!<s%> <S%H1984>Praise<s%> him with stringed <S%H4482>instruments<s%> and <S%H5748>flute!<s%>
